\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid4151349\charrsid7427796 
No.  I know I am black, and I feel that that is important, in the sense that it is a visible thing, but I think I have conditioned myself, very clearly, so that when I see another human being, I do not think of their colour fi
rst, and I never ever - and if I did so in the distant past, I can\rquote t remember when.
