\rquote 84-\rquote 85 at Warwick, went there.  But what did happen was that the Centre for Research in Ethnic Relations h
ad moved from Aston University, under John Rex, to Warwick, and Robin Cohen took over the leadership after some bust ups in the whole arrangement, much to the chagrin, of course, of John Rex.  Robin said, \'93
