\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 When you\rquote re not, in the rare moments when you\rquote re not working, what\rquote s fun for you?
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11671488 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-1871\li1871\ri113\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin113\lin1871\itap0\pararsid6571465 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid6571465\charrsid6571465 Harry:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 What do I do?  Oh!  I might have a nap, or I read a lot.  I 
read a lot of novels, particularly historical novels, and some classical text which I might have looked at but not read thoroughly, or want to revisit.  I was saying I\rquote ve been reading Gibbon's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\i\f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 Decline and Fall}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 , and I\rquote ve got this interest in novels set in t
he Roman period, and some of the texts obviously translated.  I enjoy reading, which is a continuation of what I do anyway!  (LAUGHS)  But if I\rquote m writing, or I\rquote 
m reviewing, I see that as work, and I do it in a very focused way, which is quite different from that type of reading.  But that\rquote 
s what I do.  I used to enjoy going to the theatre, and when we came last year, we went quite a bit, and we went to a number of concerts.  It\rquote s a bit lost now.  But we intend to start that up again properly.  We enjoy havi
ng dinners and entertaining people.  I don\rquote t - as Neil sometimes says, we are very remarkably boring people!  (LAUGHS)
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid11671488 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 
