\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11671488\charrsid7427796 Well, it\rquote 
s different, you see.  You have lots of relatives, I have very few.  But in a way, the process is the same.  I think one is more selective than people were in the past, and so I have two cousins in London, and I might see th
em once in five years.  We exchange cards and things like that, but my children don\rquote t seem to be interested in them.  They say, \'93Well, we don\rquote t feel we\rquote ve got anything in common\'94.  
