m sure a lot of bad things have happened to me.  There are a couple of small, tiny incidents in my life, where I have a great sense of shame.  And recently, with one of our friends in Washington, when we met in Arizona
 at this funeral, and I confessed to him it\rquote s now somewhat gone.  And you know what it was?  In 1980, I went to Dar-Es-Salaam.  When I was in the process of leaving - the family was settled in Jamaica, and I\rquote 
